('en', 'about.heading', 'Full Stack Developer passionate about technology'),
('en', 'about.paragraph1', 'I''m a full stack developer with experience in creating modern, scalable, and high-performance web applications. I''m passionate about writing clean, efficient code and transforming complex problems into simple, innovative, and robust solutions.'),
