('en', 'about.paragraph4', 'Additionally, I have 14 years of experience in support, maintenance, and systems analysis, which gives me a broad view of architecture, operations, and system behavior in production. I also have 1 year of experience as a React and Node.js developer, strengthening my full stack work.'),
